'''叠氮化铅'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式 [[铅|Pb]]([[氮|N]]<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>。和其它[[叠氮化物|叠氮化物]]一样，叠氮化铅是一种[[炸药|炸药]]，为有毒的晶状固体。

==制备和处理==
叠氮化铅可以通过[[叠氮化钠|叠氮化钠]]和[[硝酸铅|硝酸铅]]在水溶液中反应而成。<ref name=Ull>{{Ullmann|author=Jacques Boileau, Claude Fauquignon, Bernard Hueber and Hans H. Meyer|title=Explosives|year=2009|doi= 10.1002/14356007.a10_143.pub2}}</ref>反应也可以使用[[乙酸铅|乙酸铅]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lambdasyn.org/synfiles/bleiazid.htm|title=λ » LambdaSyn – Synthese von Bleiazid|website=www.lambdasyn.org|access-date=2021-12-09|archive-date=2021-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210622104708/https://lambdasyn.org/synfiles/bleiazid.htm}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Verneker | first1 = V. R. Pai | last2 = Forsyth | first2 = Arthur C. | title = Mechanism for controlling the reactivity of lead azide | journal = The Journal of Physical Chemistry | volume = 72 | pages = 111–115 | year = 1968 | doi = 10.1021/j100847a021 | url = http://www.dtic.mil/get-tr-doc/pdf?AD=AD0634629 | access-date = 2021-12-09 | archive-date = 2017-09-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170922143221/http://www.dtic.mil/get-tr-doc/pdf?AD=AD0634629 }}</ref>

通常需要将如[[糊精|糊精]]或[[聚乙烯醇|聚乙烯醇]]等增稠剂添加到溶液中，以稳定沉淀的产物。事实上，叠氮化铅通常在糊精溶液中运输，以降低其灵敏度。<ref>{{cite book |last= Fedoroff |first= Basil T. |author2=Henry A. Aaronson |author3=Earl F. Reese |author4=Oliver E. Sheffield |author5=George D. Clift  |title= Encyclopedia of Explosives and Related Items (Vol. 1) |publisher= US Army Research and Development Command TACOM, ARDEC |year= 1960 }}</ref>

==历史==
纯叠氮化铅是由{{le|西奥多·库尔提斯|Theodor Curtius}}于1891年首次制备的。由于敏感性和稳定性问题，混合糊精的叠氮化铅（IL-L-3055）于1920年代和1930年代开发。1932年，杜邦公司开始大规模生产混合糊精的叠氮化铅。<ref>{{cite book |title=Energetic Materials, Technology of the Inorganic Azides |volume=2 |publisher=Plenum Press |year=1977 |last1=Fair |first1=Harry David |last2=Walker |first2=Raymond F.}}</ref>第二次世界大战期间，雷管的发展导致需要一种输出{{le|猛度|bristance}}更高的叠氮化铅形式。RD-1333叠氮化铅（MIL-DTL-46225）是含有[[羧甲基纤维素|羧甲基纤维素]]钠的叠氮化铅，它的发展就是为了以上用途。越南战争加速了对叠氮化铅的需求，在此期间开发了专用叠氮化铅（MIL-L-14758），美国政府也开始大量囤积叠氮化铅。越南战争过后，叠氮化铅的使用急剧下降。由于美国叠氮化铅库存的规模，美国的叠氮化铅生产在1990年代初完全停止。2000年代，对库存叠氮化铅老化和稳定性的担忧促使美国政府调查处理其叠氮化铅库存的方法，并找到新的叠氮化铅制造商。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Lewis|first=T.|date=2005|title=Rolling stock safety assurance [railway safety]|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1049/ic:20050419|journal=IEE Seminar on Safety Assurance|volume=2005|page=18|publisher=IEE|doi=10.1049/ic:20050419|isbn=0-86341-574-1}}</ref>

==爆炸性==
叠氮化铅是高度敏感的，通常在绝缘橡胶容器中的水里处理和储存。它会在坠落约150毫米（6英寸）或存在7毫焦耳的静电放电后爆炸。叠氮化铅的[[爆速|爆速]]是{{convert|5180|m/s|ft/s|abbr=on}}左右。<ref>{{Cite book|last=Thurman, James T.|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/982451395|title=Practical Bomb Scene Investigation, Third Edition.|date=2017|publisher=CRC Press|isbn=978-1-351-85761-1|edition=3rd|location=Milton|oclc=982451395}}</ref>

[[乙酸铵|乙酸铵]]和[[重铬酸钠|重铬酸钠]]可以用来破坏少量的叠氮化铅。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tpub.com/gunners/7.htm|title=Primary (Initiating) Explosives|website=www.tpub.com|access-date=2017-02-13|archive-date=2021-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211209121652/http://www.tpub.com/gunners/7.htm}}</ref>

叠氮化铅会和[[铜|铜]]、[[锌|锌]]、[[镉|镉]]以及含有这些金属的合金反应，形成其它叠氮化物。举个例子，它和铜反应产生的[[叠氮化铜|叠氮化铜]]的爆炸性更强，而且敏感到不能实际使用。<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Lazari|first1=Gerasimi|last2=Stamatatos|first2=Theocharis C.|last3=Raptopoulou|first3=Catherine P.|last4=Psycharis|first4=Vassilis|last5=Pissas|first5=Michael|last6=Perlepes|first6=Spyros P.|last7=Boudalis|first7=Athanassios K.|date=2009-04-13|title=A metamagnetic 2D copper(II)-azide complex with 1D ferromagnetism and a hysteretic spin-flop transition|url=http://pubs.rsc.org/en/Content/ArticleLanding/2009/DT/b823423j#!divAbstract|journal=Dalton Transactions|language=en|issue=17|pages=3215–3221|doi=10.1039/B823423J|pmid=19421623|issn=1477-9234|access-date=2021-12-09|archive-date=2021-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211209121714/https://pubs.rsc.org/en/content/articlelanding/2009/dt/b823423j#!divAbstract}}</ref>

1981年3月30日，[[约翰·欣克利|约翰·欣克利]]在暗杀美国总统[[罗纳德·里根|罗纳德·里根]]时，用{{le|罗姆RG-14左轮手枪|Röhm RG-14}}发射了六发.22口径子弹，子弹中就含有叠氮化铅。这些子弹是由叠氮化铅中心和漆封铝弹尖组成，这种设计使得子弹撞击时发生爆炸。击中白宫新闻秘书[[詹姆斯·布雷迪|詹姆斯·布雷迪]]头部的子弹爆炸的可能性很大，而其它射到人的子弹，包括射中罗纳德·里根总统的子弹并没有爆炸。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/politics/1981/04/04/the-exploding-bullets/e1bef826-a6f5-47e9-bc32-ff3914e1747b/|title=The Exploding Bullets|first1=Pete|last1=Earley|first2=Charles|last2=Babcock|date=April 4, 1981|work=[[Washington_Post|Washington Post]]|accessdate=2021-12-09|archive-date=2022-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220108135604/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/politics/1981/04/04/the-exploding-bullets/e1bef826-a6f5-47e9-bc32-ff3914e1747b/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last1=Taubman|first1=Philip|last2=Times|first2=Special To the New York|date=1981-04-03|title=Explosive Bullet Struck Reagan, F.b.i. Discovers|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1981/04/03/us/explosive-bullet-struck-reagan-fbi-discovers.html|access-date=2020-05-18|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2022-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220108135439/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/04/03/us/explosive-bullet-struck-reagan-fbi-discovers.html}}</ref>

